{"tid":2224712,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"5鸚鵡學壞「集體講髒話」 動物園崩潰隔離懲罰","createTime":"2020-09-30T17:17:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T01:07:24.000Z","uid":15564,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ebd29ff0630390897ee202ac3e6ce50723b80985","tid":2224712,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T17:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JiehybBl9qEd6aqjl8zaKw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQyNi40/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/knYcoDqvTha.f9m0Bzuj5Q--~B/aD01MzM7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/nownews.hk/d97cabead5d652a1723ff3a5cddcde14\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FJiehybBl9qEd6aqjl8zaKw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQyNi40%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FknYcoDqvTha.f9m0Bzuj5Q--~B%2FaD01MzM7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnownews.hk%2Fd97cabead5d652a1723ff3a5cddcde14&h=05d6c976&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">英國一間動物園的鸚鵡因為太常罵髒話，被請出園區，移入不公開的鳥園「思過」。（圖／翻攝自「Lincolnshire Wildlife Park」的臉書）</span><br />\n<br />\n鸚鵡會模仿人類說話，其中非洲灰鸚鵡(African grey parrots)甚至能學舌2千個詞語。英國林肯郡野生動物園(Lincolnshire Wildlife Park)擁有1500隻鸚鵡，上個月剛接收新的一批，卻發現牠們竟會講「髒話」，當時逗得工作人員哈哈大笑，而鸚鵡開始變本加厲，還對遊客講，園方只好將牠們隔離、禁止交流。<br />\n<br />\n根據《Lincolnshire live》報導，動物園中的弗里斯科尼區(Friskney park)於2003年開放後，飼養1500多隻鸚鵡，8月15日又接受新的一批，被不同主人遺棄的5隻鸚鵡，分別是Eric，Jade，Elsie，Tyson和Billy，並安置於同一個房間，但工作人員很快就發現，這批鸚鵡竟會說「髒話」，當時逗得現場人員捧腹大笑。<br />\n<br />\n動物園執行長尼柯爾（Steve Nichols）表示，這反而會鼓勵鸚鵡繼續講，提到過去25年來，部分鸚鵡會說出下流的話（blue language），而他們早也習慣了，遊客甚至會覺得有趣，「但巧合的是，同一批接收的5隻鸚鵡全都會說，還互相學習，這意味著房間內只剩髒話，你一言我一句，而當牠們發現遊客會笑時，狀況就更嚴重了」、「每次我走過去，都會被叫胖子」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/U2MyrU2nvU4o17YYPneALQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtoPTY2Ng--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/nownews.hk/6f8ff1cc7c7ce9a7929cbb0b0b7979b4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FU2MyrU2nvU4o17YYPneALQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtoPTY2Ng--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnownews.hk%2F6f8ff1cc7c7ce9a7929cbb0b0b7979b4&h=1ed8672c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\">愛罵髒話的鸚鵡們，如今被送入獨居鳥園「反省」。（圖／翻攝自「Lincolnshire Wildlife Park」臉書）</span><br />\n<br />\n「髒話鸚鵡幫」日前還對一名少女口出惡言，即使當時遊客並未生氣，也沒感到不適，甚至覺得有趣，但下周動物園還有小孩子要來參觀，也擔心會對小朋友造成影響，因此園方決定先將牠們隔離，至少別讓3、4隻擺在一起集體爆發，「也希望牠們向周圍其他鸚鵡學習，牠們是非洲灰鸚鵡，非常善於模仿各種發聲」。<br />\n<br />\n圖/圖文：<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.nownews.com/amp/news/novelty/5073331\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fnovelty%2F5073331&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyi3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=0d40be51\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.nownews.com/amp/news/novelty/5073331</a><br />\n內文： <a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.chinatimes.com/amp/hottopic/20200930004407-260809\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Famp%2Fhottopic%2F20200930004407-260809&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyi3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=b9dc75d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.chinatimes.com/amp/hottopic/20200930004407-260809</a>"},{"pid":"fccd133172b127bfae8fe7bdadcbc09d984cf012","tid":2224712,"uid":15564,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T17:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/120184003_1111266149354053_6217479749515926368_o.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_sid=2d5d41&amp;_nc_ohc=5iRc_uwIWjsAX865HEI&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=5bb6e32197fd5036770c8412be5bd8a4&amp;oe=5F9B73F9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2